description: The deal formally ending UK membership is signed by EU leaders in Brussels.
title: Brexit: EU leaders sign UK withdrawal deal
title_page: Brexit: EU leaders sign UK withdrawal deal - BBC News
maintext: After the document was signed in Brussels it was taken to Downing Street by EU and UK officials, for signing by UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson, due later on Friday. The agreement will then travel back to Brussels, and a copy of it will remain in London.
